---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Research - Dr. Sanjeeva Reddy Dodlapati">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Research</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
        Exploring the intersection of artificial intelligence, data science, and real-world applications.
        My research focuses on developing innovative solutions that bridge theory and practice.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Research Interests</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Deep Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Advanced neural network architectures and deep learning techniques for complex pattern recognition and prediction tasks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Graph Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Graph neural networks and machine learning on graph-structured data for biological and social network analysis.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Transfer & Multi-task Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Developing models that can leverage knowledge from multiple tasks and domains to improve learning efficiency.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contrastive Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Self-supervised learning approaches using contrastive methods for representation learning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Drug Design & Discovery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Applying AI and machine learning techniques to accelerate drug discovery and molecular design processes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">DNA Methylation Prediction</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Computational methods for predicting DNA methylation patterns and their role in gene regulation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Publications</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Completing single-cell DNA methylome profiles via transfer learning together with KL-divergence</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Frontiers in Genetics • 2022</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Developed a TensorFlow-based transfer learning framework for DNA methylation prediction from genomic sequence. 
            Applied transfer learning to impute missing CpG states, boosting coverage from 1.5% to 50% in sparse methylomes.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <a href="https://doi.org/10.3389/fgene.2022.910439" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 text-sm font-medium py-2 px-3 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-50 transition-all inline-block">View Paper</a>
            <span class="text-gray-400">•</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Authors: S. Dodlapati, Z. Jiang, J. Sun</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The landscape of accessible chromatin in quiescent cardiac fibroblasts and cardiac fibroblasts activated after myocardial infarction</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Epigenetics • 2022</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Collaborative research on RNA-seq analysis of cardiac fibroblasts post-MI, identifying compensatory upregulation patterns. 
            Developed R pipelines for RNA-seq and ATAC-seq analysis to identify differentially expressed genes and open chromatin regions.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Authors: C. Li, J. Sun, Q. Liu, S. Dodlapati, H. Ming, L. Wang, Y. Li, R. Li, Z. Jiang, J. Francis, et al.</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Loss of acta2 in cardiac fibroblasts does not prevent the myofibroblast differentiation or affect the cardiac repair after myocardial infarction</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Journal of Molecular and Cellular Cardiology • 2022</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Investigation into cardiac fibroblast behavior and myofibroblast differentiation in myocardial infarction repair processes. 
            Collaborative research with LSU examining compensatory mechanisms in cardiac tissue repair.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Authors: Y. Li, C. Li, Q. Liu, L. Wang, A. X. Bao, J. P. Jung, S. Dodlapati, J. Sun, P. Gao, X. Zhang, et al.</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Syntheses of bis-triazole linked carbohydrate based macrocycles and their applications for accelerating copper sulfate mediated click reaction</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">European Journal of Organic Chemistry • 2019</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Research on synthetic methodology for carbohydrate-based macrocycles and their catalytic applications in click chemistry reactions. 
            Focus on accelerating copper-mediated reactions through novel macrocyclic structures.
          </p>
          <div class="flex space-x-4">
            <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Authors: A. Chen, L. P. Samankumara, S. Dodlapati, D. Wang, S. Adhikari, G. Wang</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Manuscripts in Preparation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Training Deep Neural Networks for DNA Methylation Prediction from DNA Sequence: A Data-centric Perspective</strong> - S. Dodlapati, J. Sun (under preparation)</li>
            <li><strong>Uncertainty-Aware Variant Effect Prediction for Genome-wide Prioritization of Non-coding Variants</strong> - S. Dodlapati, J. Sun (under preparation)</li>
            <li><strong>Learning more diverse genomic representations through hinge loss function</strong> - H. Du, S. Dodlapati, Z. Parsons, J. Sun, J. Lu (under preparation)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Current Projects</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">OmicsOracle: AI Data Agent</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Developing an AI data agent that extracts genomic data from NCBI GEO, analyzes it, extracts insights, 
            and provides visualizations. Focus on automating the genomic data analysis pipeline.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Active</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">UAVarPrior: Uncertainty-Aware Variant Prioritization</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Developing frameworks for uncertainty quantification in genomic variant effect prediction, 
            reducing computational costs by 80% while improving accuracy in variant prioritization.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Active</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">ClinicalNormBERT</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Developing a BERT model for personalized clinical text normalization, improving data extraction 
            in healthcare applications and clinical decision support systems.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Development</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Molecular Optimization Framework</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Building a comprehensive framework for molecular optimization and quantum machine learning 
            for drug discovery, integrating chemical knowledge graphs and property prediction.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Research</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Genomic Representations via Hinge Loss</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Collaborative project with UMich applying deep learning for identifying genome-wide variants 
            influencing DNA methylation, developing more diverse genomic representations.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Collaborative</span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3D Protein Structure Prediction</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Training UNet models to predict 3D protein structures from cryo-EM data, achieving performance 
            on par with existing methods while reducing computational requirements.
          </p>
          <span class="inline-block bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Development</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>